snippet.title: Space N Traders v1.09 - A Father and Sons Galaxy Adventure (PC)
snippet.description:
In this video, we show early gameplay from ‘Space N Traders’ for Steam/PC. Video was Recorded and Voiced by The Hidden Levels one and only GGIAS and GK. 

FAMILY FRIENDLY GAME THE WHOLE FAMILY CAN ENJOY FROM THE AGE OF 3 -TO- GRANDPARENTS.

SNT has a focus on teamwork with our co-pilot system which only reinforces positive response from the main pilot to the co-pilot this has been shown to help gain a bond between both players.

A positive gaming bond is a great bond that can last a life time.

Title: Space N Traders 
Developer: Digital Gamez
Publisher: Digital Gamez
Platform: Steam/PC
Release Date: TBA
Official Site:  sntvideogame.com
Digital Gamez Discord: https://discord.gg/XnmcXpG
Store link: https://digitalgamez.itch.io/space-n-traders-demo

The Hidden Levels is fully committed to bringing you the greatest and best entertainment through means of Twitch, YouTube and all other forms of active media.  We live stream to twitch and upload videos to YouTube daily. The Hidden Levels consists of gamers from all around the world. For more info please visit:

Website: http://www.thehiddenlevels.com
